(156, 2, 'WeCare Flex Mais', '&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 12.727272033691406px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Motorista com Seguro!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 12.727272033691406px;&quot;&gt;O cliente compra seu pacote com uma agenda completa e escolhe os outros serviços somente na hora que precisar, inclusive motorista sendo uma utilização por serviço, totalizando até 3 serviços diferentes no ano.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;10&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12.727272033691406px; width: 850px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td rowspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wecareauto.com.br/image/data/agenda-carro.jpg&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em; opacity: 0.9; width: 150px; height: 75px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td colspan=&quot;5&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;p class=&quot;Padr3fo&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 13px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Agenda do&amp;nbsp;veículo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p class=&quot;Padr3fo&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 13px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;A partir do momento em que o seu carro entra&amp;nbsp;para a WeCare,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;nossos especialistas passam&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;a monitorar tudo o que acontece com ele,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;como:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;inspeção veicular,&amp;nbsp;recalls, revisões, licencimanto, renovação de CNH, IPVA e DPVAT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;s